her=InterVarsity Press |ref=harv |page=[https://archive.org/details/jesusmiraclework00grah/page/95 95] }}\n* {{cite book|last=Van Voorst|first=Robert E|year=2000|title=Jesus Outside the New Testament: An Introduction to the Ancient Evidence|publisher=Eerdmans Publishing|isbn=978-0-8028-4368-5| url=https://books.google.com/?id=lwzliMSRGGkC |ref=harv}}\n* {{cite book|title=Expository Dictionary of New Testament Words|last= Vine | first= William E. | authorlink= William Edwy Vine |year= 1940|publisher= Fleming H. Revell Company|ref=harv |isbn= 978-0-916441-31-9}}\n* {{cite book |title= Jesus the Jew: A Historian's Reading of the Gospels|edition= |last= Vermes|first= Geza|authorlink1= Geza Vermes|year= 1981|publisher= First Fortress|location= Philadelphia|isbn= 978-0-8006-1443-0 |url=https://books.google.com/?id=RvSEK2HALnwC|ref=harv}}\n* {{cite book|title= The Authentic Gospel of Jesus|edition= |last= Vermes|first= Geza|authorlink1= Geza Vermes|year= 2003|publisher= Penguin|location= London|isbn= 978-0-14-100360-3|url= https://archive.org/details/authenticgospelo00verm}}\n* {{cite book|title=The Bible Knowledge Commentary: New Testament| first1=John F. |last1=Walvoord | authorlink1=John Walvoord|first2= Roy B.|last2= Zuck|year= 1983 |isbn= 978-0-88207-812-0|publisher=David C. Cook|url=https://books.google.com/?id=DP4UiA4gQNMC |ref=harv}}\n* {{cite book|last=Wilson|first=Barrie A|authorlink1=Barrie Wilson|year=2007|title=How Jesus Became Christian|publisher=St.Martin's Press|location=New York|isbn=978-0-679-31493-6|url-access=registration|url=https://archive.org/details/howjesusbecamech00barr}}\n* {{cite book|title=The Jesus Quest: The Third Search for the Jew of Nazareth|first= Ben|last= Witherington |author-link=Ben Witherington III|year= 1997| isbn= 978-0-8308-1544-9 |ref=harv |publisher=InterVarsity Press |url=https://books.google.com/?id=IE_T3Xh2fyUC}}\n{{refend}}\n\n== External links ==\n{{Spoken Wikipedia|Jesus Spoken Version.ogg|October 28, 2013}}\n* {{curlie|Society/Religion_and_Spirituality/Christianity/Jesus_Christ/}}\n* [http://www.latinvulgate.com/christverse.aspx Complete Sayings of Jesus Christ] in parallel Latin and English.\n\n{{Jesus footer |state=expanded}}\n{{Navboxes|list=\n{{Christmas}}\n{{Easter}}\n{{Nativity of Jesus}}\n{{Virgin Mary}}\n{{Apostles}}\n{{New Testament people|prophets}}\n{{Prophets in the Qur'an}}\n{{Christianity footer}}\n{{Religion topics}}\n{{Gospel of Matthew}}\n{{Gospel of Mark}}\n{{Gospel of Luke}}\n{{Gospel of John}}\n{{Acts of the Apostles}}\n{{Titles of Jesus}}\n}}\n{{Subject bar\n|book1    = Jesus\n|portal1  = Christianity\n|portal2  = Islam\n|portal3  = Religion\n|commons  = y\n|commons-search = \u05d9\u05e9\u05d5\u05e2\n|wikt     = y\n|wikt-search = Jesus\n|b        = y\n|b-search = Biblical Studies/Christianity/Jesus\n|q        = y\n|s        = y\n|s-search = Author:Jesus of Nazareth\n|v        = y\n|d        = y\n|v-search = Jesus\n|d-search = Q302\n}}\n{{Authority control}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Jesus}}\n[[Category:0s BC births]]\n[[Category:30s deaths]]\n[[Category:1st-century apocalypticists]]\n[[Category:1st-century BCE Jews]]\n[[Category:1st-century BC Romans]]\n[[Category:1st-century executions]]\n[[Category:1st-century rabbis]]\n[[Category:1st-century Romans]]\n[[Category:Angelic visionaries]]\n[[Category:Christianity]]\n[[Category:Creator gods]]\n[[Category:Deified people]]\n[[Category:Exorcists]]\n[[Category:Founders of religions]]\n[[Category:God in Christianity]]\n[[Category:Jesus| ]]\n[[Category:Jewish Messiah claimants]]\n[[Category:Judean people]]\n[[Category:Life-death-rebirth gods]]\n[[Category:Messianism]]\n[[Category:People considered avatars by their followers]]\n[[Category:People executed by crucifixion]]\n[[Category:People executed by the Roman Empire]]\n[[Category:People from Bethlehem]]\n[[Category:People from Nazareth]]\n[[Category:Prophets in Islam]]\n[[Category:Prophets of Islam]]\n[[Category:Prophets of the New Testament]]\n[[Category:Philosophers of ethics 